# Blog Content Directory

This directory will contain MDX blog posts organized by year.

Structure:
```
blog/
├── 2024/
│   ├── post-slug-1.mdx
│   └── post-slug-2.mdx
├── 2025/
│   └── another-post.mdx
└── authors/
    ├── author-1.json
    └── author-2.json
```

MDX files are generated automatically by the blog automation system in `scripts/blog-automation/`.